      <p>McBride II, Curtis Dale Owner</p>
      <p>Alpha Tree Service</p>
      <p>License: ALPHATS84409</p>
      <p>Effective: 09/29/2016</p>
      <p>Experation: 10/07/2024</p>
      <p>Address: P.O. Box2506, Belfair, WA 98528</p>
    </div>

